Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.90,0:00:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错嘛\N去了哪里旅游
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.57,0:00:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热海\N热海？真好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.97,0:00:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和女朋友吗？\N不是，普通的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.38,0:00:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没有女朋友啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.92,0:00:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.65,0:00:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你呢\N我没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.86,0:00:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不受女生欢迎的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.52,0:00:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有美女的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.93,0:00:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿不是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.00,0:00:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看这个/N是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.15,0:00:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过都没联系的了\N不错嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.55,0:00:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.95,0:01:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈欢迎回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.16,0:01:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好啊\N你好，初次见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.96,0:01:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫大田\N你好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.03,0:01:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你们倒茶去，请稍等哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.17,0:01:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦了哦\N没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.11,0:01:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妈妈不错嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.11,0:01:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我她总是穿和服的\N哦是啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.93,0:01:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.13,0:01:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前你交过女朋友吗\N久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.54,0:01:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.75,0:02:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我交过2任女友\N哦厉害嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.02,0:02:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要交女朋友啊\N哦哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.97,0:02:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你穿和服好漂亮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.84,0:02:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真会说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.04,0:02:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请喝茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.24,0:02:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.11,0:02:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说真的\N好漂亮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.11,0:02:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.91,0:02:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们慢玩\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.65,0:02:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道什么时候出现我的女朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.12,0:02:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.33,0:02:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望不会等太久啊\N是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.00,0:02:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妈妈真有气质啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.07,0:02:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.74,0:03:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要想什么奇怪的念头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.61,0:03:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是我妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.21,0:03:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这么漂亮吗\N是啊我很少看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.35,0:03:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太诱人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.42,0:03:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要那样说\N啊是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.43,0:03:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.03,0:03:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美丽的和服的熟女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.07,0:04:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谦治，你怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.54,0:04:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.82,0:04:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么突然穿起了和服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.63,0:04:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊，就是想穿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.16,0:04:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他们说你好诱人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.77,0:04:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢\N哪里有哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.97,0:04:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜欢吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.57,0:04:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谦治想做吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.24,0:04:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想\N想的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.11,0:04:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.52,0:04:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈对你温柔点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.41,0:05:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手模哪里哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.61,0:05:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手模哪里哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.48,0:06:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.62,0:06:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谦治，不要那么急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.49,0:06:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈也摸我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.36,0:06:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和儿子谦治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.83,0:06:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他青春期来的时候\N我们发生了那个关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.63,0:06:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那以后\N我们就常常一起做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.57,0:06:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会觉得异常的兴奋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.52,0:07:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.59,0:07:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.46,0:07:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里做吧\N这里吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.09,0:07:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒大了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.86,0:08:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.47,0:08:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 舒服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.80,0:08:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.71,0:09:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像平时那样，蛋蛋也舔吧\N蛋蛋吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.89,0:09:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样，舒服吗\N舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.99,0:10:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要急\N啊妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.26,0:10:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要一会呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.54,0:10:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿你没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.14,0:11:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.44,0:13:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服\N舒服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.51,0:13:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.53,0:14:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.66,0:14:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等等哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.67,0:15:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不冷吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.22,0:15:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等等哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.20,0:16:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能说出去的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.00,0:16:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N保密我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.44,0:17:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.10,0:18:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谦治\N要保密哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.03,0:18:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.57,0:20:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谦治\N我害羞哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.71,0:22:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谦治\N妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.98,0:22:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.65,0:22:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要高潮啊\N高潮啊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.28,0:23:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来舔你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:13.41,0:25:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈一起舔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:15.14,0:25:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:24.35,0:25:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:16.14,0:26:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谦治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:18.14,0:26:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:32.02,0:26:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:07.79,0:27:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:10.32,0:27:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:18.87,0:27:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谦治进去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:29.94,0:27:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:24.66,0:28:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:23.12,0:29:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让妈妈放进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:29.53,0:29:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:40.07,0:29:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谦治好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:40.67,0:30:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谦治好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:02.96,0:31:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:38.06,0:31:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要高潮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:40.59,0:31:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高潮阿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:09.96,0:32:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈在上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:37.05,0:32:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:20.96,0:33:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊舒服啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:40.23,0:36:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:08.12,0:37:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊妈妈好舒服啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:16.13,0:37:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:19.20,0:37:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿妈妈我要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:15.25,0:38:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了拿电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:20.99,0:38:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上再去谦治家拿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:38.21,0:38:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然就这样走了\N是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:42.75,0:38:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃木的太太真是可I隘啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:46.09,0:38:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，要自己负担起家计
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:48.62,0:38:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这也是没办法的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:51.02,0:38:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这生死也是没办法的\N是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:55.29,0:38:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是去得太早了啊\N孩子都还小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:00.77,0:39:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，孩子都那么小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:04.10,0:39:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人也不是那么容易抚养的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:06.77,0:39:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很不容易的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:09.31,0:39:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:13.71,0:39:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法的啊\N老公你工作也要小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:17.18,0:39:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:25.32,0:39:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:26.93,0:39:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天不出去吧\N我不出去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:32.53,0:39:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:33.47,0:39:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是大田的电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:36.40,0:39:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许他一会\N会回来拿电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:40.54,0:39:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:42.54,0:39:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要出门吗\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:45.08,0:39:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和朋友谈谈旅行的细节\N哦是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:49.62,0:39:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谦治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:51.48,0:39:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个电话放在客厅的桌子上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:56.02,0:39:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样比较显眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:58.82,0:40:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拿过去放着吧\N那我走了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:01.76,0:40:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你走好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:03.23,0:40:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我放这里\N好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:16.04,0:40:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是累啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:25.12,0:40:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:27.92,0:40:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明夭要出差啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:30.32,0:40:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公要出差吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:32.06,0:40:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少天？\N3天吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:34.73,0:40:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:36.06,0:40:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公，谦治明天要旅行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:41.40,0:40:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:43.80,0:40:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里只有我一个人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:18.77,0:41:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:21.71,0:41:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:25.98,0:41:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:28.11,0:41:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会谦治就回来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:31.72,0:41:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到就不好了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:34.92,0:41:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就动作快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:38.26,0:41:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要想他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:41.59,0:41:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个地方申兴奋呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:49.20,0:41:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:55.47,0:41:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面湿了哦\N咽日有哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:14.29,0:42:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公在这里不好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:18.56,0:42:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有人来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:40.85,0:42:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:15.02,0:43:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴奋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:17.82,0:43:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是
